(1361, 261, '_elementor_data', '[{"id":"7a3b54f","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInLeft"},"elements":[{"id":"7e51c85","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","background_hover_transition":{"unit":"px","size":1}},"elements":[{"id":"f32c308","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>La Maison Kammerzell<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4><p>Id\\u00e9alement situ\\u00e9 au pied de la Cath\\u00e9drale de Strasbourg, au c\\u0153ur de l\\u2019Europe, la c\\u00e9l\\u00e8bre Maison Kammerzell est un lieu incontournable \\u00e0 visiter.<\\/p><p>Consid\\u00e9r\\u00e9e comme \\u00ab la plus belle maison de Strasbourg \\u00bb, elle symbolise des splendeurs s\\u00e9culaires de la ville qui en tire une grande fiert\\u00e9.<\\/p><p>Elle est l\\u2019une des plus belles brasseries du monde et vous propose ce dimanche 15 avril \\u00e0 9h45 une visite guid\\u00e9e afin de d\\u00e9couvrir tous les d\\u00e9tails de sa construction et son histoire.<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes","align_mobile":"justify","text_color":"#54595f","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":14},"_background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"a2353de","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"caae1de","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/4864510031_768bc2605d-e1521545781809.jpg","id":238},"image_size":"full","align_tablet":"center","link_to":"custom","link":{"url":"https:\\/\\/www.maison-kammerzell.com\\/","is_external":"","nofollow":""},"space_mobile":{"unit":"%","size":47},"_background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"91c2f7b","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_background":"classic","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInRight"},"elements":[{"id":"467c1b7","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"6f9a95b","elType":"widget","settings":{"space":{"unit":"px","size":0}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"},{"id":"afd1de4","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>L'' Atelier des chefs<br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4><p>Vous allez aimer cuisiner !<\\/p><p>Apprenti cordon bleu en recherche de perfectionnement ou d\\u00e9butant, ou simplement Chef du jour, nos cours s''adaptent \\u00e0 tous les profils. Curieux, \\u00e9picuriens, gourmands et gourmets, vous trouverez tous la formule faite pour vous. Mettez la main \\u00e0 la p\\u00e2te et vivez un pur moment de gourmandise.<\\/p><p>Prenez possession des fourneaux le temps d''un cours, d\\u00e9gustez vos r\\u00e9alisations autour de nos tables d''h\\u00f4tes, d\\u00e9ambulez dans notre boutique. Lieux de vie, de partage et de plaisir, poussez la porte de notre atelier... vous allez vous r\\u00e9galer !<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes","text_color":"#54595f","_background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"99d6e1e","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"a391145","elType":"widget","settings":{"space":{"unit":"px","size":0},"space_tablet":{"unit":"px","size":0}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"},{"id":"b68bd3a","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/atelier_des_chefs.jpg","id":117},"image_size":"full","align_tablet":"center","link_to":"custom","link":{"url":"https:\\/\\/www.atelierdeschefs.fr\\/fr\\/agenda-cours-cuisine-strasbourg.php","is_external":"","nofollow":""},"space_tablet":{"unit":"%","size":100},"space_mobile":{"unit":"%","size":47},"_margin_tablet":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true},"_padding_tablet":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true},"_background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"ebea9c2","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInLeft"},"elements":[{"id":"170934f","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"18581bc","elType":"widget","settings":{"space":{"unit":"px","size":0}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"},{"id":"95a063e","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Stride<br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4><p>Bienvenue dans le plus grand Bike Park Indoor d''Europe !<\\/p><p>Ouvert \\u00e0 tous, d\\u00e8s 3 ans, STRIDE propose les meilleurs \\u00e9quipements pour d\\u00e9couvrir, s''exercer ou vivre une exp\\u00e9rience v\\u00e9lo.<\\/p><p>Ce Bike Park de 12 000 m\\u00b2 est un lieu de loisir permettant \\u00e0 chacun de progresser dans la pratique du VTT ou du BMX dans les meilleures conditions.<\\/p><p>STRIDE se compose de diff\\u00e9rentes zones permettant des pratiques diff\\u00e9rentes et vari\\u00e9es du deux roues : Cross Country, Maniabilit\\u00e9, Park, R\\u00e9sille, Bac \\u00e0 mousse, Pumptrack, Initiation et Mini Stride.<\\/p><p>Venez avec votre v\\u00e9lo ou louez en un sur place.<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes","text_color":"#54595f"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"8a8c46b","elType"