(1606, 303, '_elementor_data', '[{"id":"7a3b54f","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInLeft"},"elements":[{"id":"7e51c85","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","background_hover_transition":{"unit":"px","size":1}},"elements":[{"id":"f32c308","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>La Maison Kammerzell<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\"font-family:Aref Ruqaa;\\">Id\\u00e9alement situ\\u00e9 au pied de la Cath\\u00e9drale de Strasbourg, au c\\u0153ur de l\\u2019Europe, la c\\u00e9l\\u00e8bre Maison Kammerzell est un lieu incontournable \\u00e0 visiter.\\n\\nConsid\\u00e9r\\u00e9e comme \\u00ab la plus belle maison de Strasbourg \\u00bb, elle symbolise des splendeurs s\\u00e9culaires de la ville qui en tire une grande fiert\\u00e9.\\n\\nElle est l\\u2019une des plus belles brasseries du monde et vous propose ce dimanche 15 avril \\u00e0 9h45 une visite guid\\u00e9e afin de d\\u00e9couvrir tous les d\\u00e9tails de sa construction et son histoire.<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes","align_mobile":"justify","text_color":"#54595f","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":14},"_background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"a2353de","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"caae1de","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/4864510031_768bc2605d-e1521545781809.jpg","id":238},"image_size":"full","align_tablet":"center","link_to":"custom","link":{"url":"https:\\/\\/www.maison-kammerzell.com\\/","is_external":"","nofollow":""},"space_mobile":{"unit":"%","size":47},"_background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"c653eeb","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInRight","shape_divider_top_color":"#f6f0e5","margin":{"unit":"px","top":"10","right":0,"bottom":"10","left":0,"isLinked":true},"margin_tablet":{"unit":"px","top":"20","right":0,"bottom":"20","left":0,"isLinked":true},"margin_mobile":{"unit":"px","top":"40","right":0,"bottom":"40","left":0,"isLinked":true}},"elements":[{"id":"ffe4cc8","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center","padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true}},"elements":[{"id":"2570cc0","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>L'' Atelier des chefs\\n<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\"font-family:Aref Ruqaa;\\">Vous allez aimer cuisiner !\\n\\nApprenti cordon bleu en recherche de perfectionnement ou d\\u00e9butant, ou simplement Chef du jour, nos cours s''adaptent \\u00e0 tous les profils. Curieux, \\u00e9picuriens, gourmands et gourmets, vous trouverez tous la formule faite pour vous. Mettez la main \\u00e0 la p\\u00e2te et vivez un pur moment de gourmandise.\\n\\nPrenez possession des fourneaux le temps d''un cours, d\\u00e9gustez vos r\\u00e9alisations autour de nos tables d''h\\u00f4tes, d\\u00e9ambulez dans notre boutique. Lieux de vie, de partage et de plaisir, poussez la porte de notre atelier... vous allez vous r\\u00e9galer !<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"0893e09","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"f0a6a07","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/atelier_des_chefs.jpg","id":117}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"6c0f662","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInLeft"},"elements":[{"id":"edcaab2","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"c91efd2","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Stride\\n<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\"font-family:Aref Ruqaa;\\">Bienvenue dans le plus grand Bike Park Indoor d''Europe !\\n\\nOuvert \\u00e0 tous, d\\u00e8s 3 ans, STRIDE propose les meilleurs \\u00e9quipements pour d\\u00e9couvrir, s''exercer ou vivre une exp\\u00e9rience v\\u00e9lo.\\n\\nCe Bike Park de 12 000 m\\u00b2 est un lieu de loisir permettant \\u00e0 chacun de progresser dans la pratique du VTT ou du BMX dans les meilleures conditions.\\n\\nSTRIDE se compose de diff\\u00e9rentes zones permettant des pratiques diff\\u00e9rentes et vari\\u00e9es du deux roues : Cross Country, Maniabilit\\u00e9, Park, R\\u00e9sille, Bac \\u00e0 mousse, Pumptrack, Initiation et Mini Stride.\\n\\nVenez avec votre v\\u00e9lo ou louez en un sur place.<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"c44001d","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"4f474b7","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/stride-1.jpg","id":244}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"90be91b","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_background":"classic","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInRight","margin_tablet":{"unit":"px","top":"20","right":0,"bottom":"20","left":0,"isLinked":true},"margin_mobile":{"unit":"px","top":"40","right":0,"bottom":"40","left":0,"isLinked":true}},"elements":[{"id":"95787a2","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"9cacec7","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Food &amp; City\\u00a0 Tours<br \\/> <\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\"font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\">Food &amp; City Tours est un organisateur de visites guid\\u00e9es immersives dans le centre historique strasbourgeois. La visite guid\\u00e9e devient ludique et conviviale, chaque participant sera invit\\u00e9 \\u00e0 d\\u00e9guster des sp\\u00e9cialit\\u00e9s alsaciennes pendant son parcours p\\u00e9destre dans le c\\u0153ur de Strasbourg.<\\/p><p>Accompagn\\u00e9 d\\u2019un guide conf\\u00e9rencier dipl\\u00f4m\\u00e9, le visiteur d\\u00e9couvrira \\u00e0 la fois l\\u2019histoire de la capitale alsacienne tout en se r\\u00e9galant de produits du terroir g\\u00e9n\\u00e9reusement servis par des commer\\u00e7ants passionn\\u00e9s qui prendront le temps de partager leur passion pour l\\u2019Alsace.<\\/p><p>Une exp\\u00e9rience authentique, d\\u2019ores et d\\u00e9j\\u00e0 test\\u00e9e et approuv\\u00e9e par de nombreux voyageurs.<\\/p><p>Retrouvez toute l\\u2019offre Food &amp; City Tours sur le site : www.foodandcitytours.com (multilingue). Inscription possible en ligne.<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"3e0c28e","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"988fe15","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/FoodCity_Tours-1.jpg","id":246}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"c06ded8","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInLeft"},"elements":[{"id":"a576bcd","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"48a2e24","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Dooz Escape Game\\n<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\"font-family:Aref Ruqaa;\\">Dooz Escape Game vous fera vivre une exp\\u00e9rience intense dans diff\\u00e9rentes \\u00e9poques avec ses d\\u00e9cors immersifs, ses personnages et ses \\u00e9nigmes. Chaque mission s''inscrit dans un univers sc\\u00e9naris\\u00e9 dont vous \\u00eates l''un des h\\u00e9ros, mais attention \\u00e0 tous ceux se mettant sur votre route !\\n\\nDooz Escape Game est un jeu d''\\u00e9vasion grandeur nature.\\nVous aurez entre 45 ou 60 minutes pour vous \\u00e9chapper d''une de nos \\"rooms\\" en fouillant des pi\\u00e8ces pour trouver des indices et r\\u00e9soudre des \\u00e9nigmes en s\\u00e9rie.\\n\\nPr\\u00e9vu de 2 \\u00e0 6 joueurs, le jeu ne demande pas d''efforts physique ou de connaissances particuli\\u00e8res ; il sa base sur la logique et la coop\\u00e9ration entre joueurs.\\n\\nOserez-vous tenter l''aventure, voyageurs ?<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"0c22dc4","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"0e4495e","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/Dooz-logo.png","id":245}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"aeb1d71","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22","background_hover_background":"classic","background_hover_color":"#f6f0e5","animation":"fadeInRight","margin_tablet":{"unit":"px","top":"20","right":0,"bottom":"20","left":0,"isLinked":true}},"elements":[{"id":"92968fa","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"e0fad44","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h4 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Le Spa \\u00ab \\u00d4 fil de l''eau \\u00bb<br \\/> <\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\"font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\">Le spa \\u00ab \\u00d4 fil de l''eau \\u00bb est d\\u00e9di\\u00e9 au plaisir des sens et des \\u00e9motions. Il allie bien-\\u00eatre, esth\\u00e9tique et beaut\\u00e9 sur un espace de 200 m\\u00b2 contenant un sauna, un hammam ainsi qu''une douche sensorielle.<\\/p><p>La terrasse permet de se plonger dans l''eau d''un bain relaxant ou de se pr\\u00e9lasser sur des chaises longues tout en savourant une vue imprenable sur les maisons \\u00e0 colombages qui bordent la rivi\\u00e8re de l''Ill.<\\/p><p>En association avec la marque Cinq Mondes, diff\\u00e9rent soins, modelages, gommages et rituels sont propos\\u00e9s pour le corps et le visage, dans une cabine simple ou double pour partager une exp\\u00e9rience unique \\u00e0 deux.<\\/p><p>Les jeunes \\u00e2g\\u00e9s entre 12 et 18 ans peuvent b\\u00e9n\\u00e9ficier d''une carte de soins sp\\u00e9cialement con\\u00e7us pour eux.<\\/p>","drop_cap":"yes","_margin_tablet":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"ec41bb3","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null,"content_position":"center"},"elements":[{"id":"2903eba","elType":"widget","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/03\\/223012596_1.jpg","id":250},"image_size":"custom","image_custom_dimension":{"width":"700","height":"1000"},"align":"center","link_to":"custom","link":{"url":"http:\\/\\/www.regent-petite-france.com\\/spa-fitness\\/","is_external":"","nofollow":""}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"image"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false}]'),
