<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">Fort modeste au d\\u00e9part, le bourg s\\u2019affirme sous le r\\u00e8gne des Carolingiens comme le carrefour des civilisations rh\\u00e9nanes.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">Strasbourg fut l\\u2019une des premi\\u00e8res villes \\u00e0 se d\\u00e9barrasser de la tutelle des \\u00e9v\\u00eaques, la bourgeoisie commer\\u00e7ante s\\u2019affirmant comme le vrai pouvoir.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> La construction de la cath\\u00e9drale ira de pair avec une prosp\\u00e9rit\\u00e9 grandissante.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> Le dynamisme \\u00e9conomique de la ville se double d''un bouillonnement intellectuel et culturel.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">Strasbourg, capitale de l\\u2019Europe et de l\\u2019Alsace, poss\\u00e8de un patrimoine historique et architectural qui en fait la ville la plus riche d\\u2019Alsace.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> Son centre ville fait partie du patrimoine mondial de L\\u2019UNESCO et ses mus\\u00e9es sont particuli\\u00e8rement riches et int\\u00e9ressants.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">L\\u2019histoire de la ville de Strasbourg est indissociable de l\\u2019histoire d\\u2019Alsace et, plus largement de la vall\\u00e9e du Rhin.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> Elle s\\u2019inscrit \\u00e9galement dans l\\u2019histoire de l\\u2019Europe, entre France et Allemagne, royaumes, empires ou r\\u00e9publiques.<\\/span><\\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"359a72a","elType":"widget","settings":[],"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"9b97d5f","elType":"section","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"84165ca","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100},"elements":[{"id":"d048664","elType":"widget","settings":[],"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"c151ec5","elType":"section","settings":{"background_hover_background":"classic","animation":"fadeInUp","content_position":"middle"},"elements":[{"id":"bdb9732","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100,"background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[{"id":"ee5fd04","elType":"widget","settings":{"wp":{"title":"A LA UNE","number_posts":"1","post_title_length":"1000","category_label":"In","excerpt_length":"55","excerpt_more":" [\\u2026]","category_ids":["0"],"show_thumb":"on","thumb_dimensions":"medium","thumb_width":"800","thumb_height":"100","default_url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/recent-posts-widget-with-thumbnails\\/default_thumb.gif"},"_background_hover_background":"classic"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"wp-widget-recent-posts-widget-with-thumbnails"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false}]'),
