text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">\\u00c0 partir de 496, les Francs, ma\\u00eetres de l\\u2019Alsace, font surgir une nouvelle ville, Strateburgum (\\u00ab\\u00a0ville forte des routes\\u00a0\\u00bb).<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">Fort modeste au d\\u00e9part, le bourg s\\u2019affirme sous le r\\u00e8gne des Carolingiens comme le carrefour des civilisations rh\\u00e9nanes.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">Strasbourg fut l\\u2019une des premi\\u00e8res villes \\u00e0 se d\\u00e9barrasser de la tutelle des \\u00e9v\\u00eaques, la bourgeoisie commer\\u00e7ante s\\u2019affirmant comme le vrai pouvoir.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> La construction de la cath\\u00e9drale ira de pair avec une prosp\\u00e9rit\\u00e9 grandissante.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> Le dynamisme \\u00e9conomique de la ville se double d''un bouillonnement intellectuel et culturel.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">Strasbourg, capitale de l\\u2019Europe et de l\\u2019Alsace, poss\\u00e8de un patrimoine historique et architectural qui en fait la ville la plus riche d\\u2019Alsace.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> Son centre ville fait partie du patrimoine mondial de L\\u2019UNESCO et ses mus\\u00e9es sont particuli\\u00e8rement riches et int\\u00e9ressants.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: left; font-family: Aref Ruqaa;\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\">L\\u2019histoire de la ville de Strasbourg est indissociable de l\\u2019histoire d\\u2019Alsace et, plus largement de la vall\\u00e9e du Rhin.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"color: #ffffff;\\"> Elle s\\u2019inscrit \\u00e9galement dans l\\u2019histoire de l\\u2019Europe, entre France et Allemagne, royaumes, empires ou r\\u00e9publiques.<\\/span><\\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"359a72a","elType":"widget","settings":[],"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"9b97d5f","elType":"section","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"84165ca","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100},"elements":[{"id":"d048664","elType":"widget","settings":[],"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"49d09a8","elType":"section","settings":{"_element_id":"recent_post_container"},"elements":[{"id":"869096a","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100},"elements":[{"id":"d6dd5e4","elType":"widget","settings":{"wp":{"title":"A LA UNE","title_url":"http:\\/\\/strasbourg.sandrine-alcazar.com\\/actualites","cssID":"recent_post","css_class":"","before":"","after":"","ignore_sticky":"on","exclude_current":"on","post_type":["post"],"post_status":"publish","order":"DESC","orderby":"date","taxonomy":"","limit":"1","offset":"0","thumb":"on","thumb_height":"180","thumb_width":"280","thumb_align":"rpwe-alignleft","thumb_default":"http:\\/\\/placehold.it\\/45x45\\/f0f0f0\\/ccc","length":"20","readmore":"on","readmore_text":"Lire la suite...","comment_count":"on","date":"on","css":"#recent_post_container {\\r\\ndisplay:flex;\\r\\nflex-direction:column;\\r\\njustify-content:center;\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\n.rpwe-block ul{\\r\\n    list-style: none !important;\\r\\n    margin-left: 0 !important;\\r\\n    padding-left: 0 !important;\\r\\n\\r\\n    \\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\n.rpwe-block li{\\r\\n    display:flex;\\r\\n    flex-direction:column;\\r\\njustify-content:center;\\r\\nalign-items:center;\\r\\n    border:none;\\r\\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\\r\\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\\r\\n    list-style-type: none;\\r\\n\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\n.elementor-widget-container h5 {\\r\\n    margin-bottom:30px;\\r\\n    text-align: center;\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\n.elementor-widget-container h5 a {\\r\\n    color:#3C4858;\\r\\n}\\r\\n\\r\\n.rpwe-block {\\r\\n\\r\